              <strong>Example:</strong> If we use OpenAI's GPT models or other third-party AI providers, your data is subject to their terms as well. Review third-party terms carefully before use.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 16. Compliance with Laws -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark dark:text-white mb-4">16. Compliance with Laws</h2>
          
          <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6 mb-4">
            You agree to use our Services in compliance with all applicable laws, including:
          </p>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white mb-3">In India:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-body-color dark:text-dark-6 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Information Technology Act, 2000</li>
              <li>Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023</li>
              <li>Consumer Protection Act, 2019</li>
              <li>Applicable GST regulations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white mb-3">Internationally:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-body-color dark:text-dark-6 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>GDPR (EU/UK)</li>
              <li>CCPA (California)</li>
              <li>Data protection laws in your jurisdiction</li>
              <li>Export control and sanctions regulations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 17. Severability -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark dark:text-white mb-4">17. Severability</h2>
          
          <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6">
            If any provision of these Terms is found invalid or unenforceable, that provision will be modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it valid, or if not possible, severed. The remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 18. Entire Agreement -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark dark:text-white mb-4">18. Entire Agreement</h2>
          
          <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6">
            These Terms, together with our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="/legal-notice" class="text-primary hover:underline">Legal Notice</a>, constitute the entire agreement between you and PAL Portals regarding the Services and supersede all prior and contemporaneous agreements and understandings.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 19. Contact Information -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark dark:text-white mb-4">19. Contact Information</h2>
          
          <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6 mb-4">
            For questions or concerns regarding these Terms of Services, please contact:
          </p>

          <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6 mb-2">
